---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-waqf-green-dark text-white pt-20 pb-8 relative overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-waqf-gold">
  <!-- Subtiel patroon -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-islamic-pattern opacity-5 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">

      <!-- Kolom 1: Over / Logo -->
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <img
            src="/images/logo/footer_dark (8).png"
            alt="Ummah.be"
            class="h-12 w-auto"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          De digitale fundering voor de Belgische Ummah. Wij bouwen en onderhouden professionele, toekomstbestendige websites voor moskee&euml;n in de Benelux.
        </p>
        <!-- Socials -->
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-waqf-gold transition" aria-label="LinkedIn">
